Package org.vngx.jsch.config

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SSHConfigConstants
    Interface to define configuration property name constants along with their respective descriptions.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BooleanPropertyValidator
    Implementation of PropertyValidator which validates a property value by checking if it's a boolean.
    JSchConfig
    JSchConfig is a singleton of a global configuration for setting and retrieving vngx-jsch library configuration properties.
    NumberPropertyValidator
    Implementation of PropertyValidator for validating numeric properties values.
    PropertyValidator
    Simple property value validator which provides two methods; one to check if a given property value is valid, and another to return a default value for a property.
    SessionConfig
    SessionConfig allows the user to specify configuration properties for an instance of Session.
    StringSetPropertyValidator
    Implementation of PropertyValidator which validates by checking if a string property is contained in the set of allowed values passed to the constructor.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidPropertyException
    An exception which can be thrown when an invalid property value has been found.
